<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.9">
<l>poṉkulām payalai pūttaṉa mentōḷ porukayal kaṇtuyil maṟantāḷ</l>
<l>aṉpiṉā luṉmē lātaram peritiv vaṇaṅkiṉuk kuṟṟanō yaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>miṉkulā maruṅkul curuṅkamēl neruṅki vīṅkiya vaṉamulai yāḷuk</l>
<l>keṉkolāṅ kuṟippi leṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A gold-like pallor appears on [her] soft shoulders;</l>
<l rend="indent">she shuns sleep [for] her eyes, [which are] like warring fish.</l>
<l>[Her] desire is great with love toward you;</l>
<l rend="indent">I don’t understand the disease which has befallen this divine being.</l>
<l>What will happen to her whose lovely breasts have swelled,</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing down [from] above, as her lightning-like waist dwindles?</l>
<l>What were you thinking in your inner thoughts, lord father of Iṭaventai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
